snippet.title: Cats are simply funny, clumsy and cute! - Funny cat compilation
snippet.description:
Cats are simply the funniest animals! Who doesn't like cats?! Cats and kittens make us laugh, smile and happy! Just look how they play, sleep, make funny sounds, fail, get scared, play with other animals, react to mirrors, toasters,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
